Sofitel Marseille Vieux Port
     __________________________________________________________________

   “

   Welcome to Sofitel Marseille Vieux Port, a haven of peace in the heart
   of the “Cité Phocéenne”. Here you may admire the most beautiful view in
   Marseille, savour some of the region’s most mouth-watering cuisine, and
   indulge in some truly amazing cocktails on our rooftop.
   „
   Paul Barthe
   The General Manager
   36 boulevard Charles Livon
   13007 Marseille
   Tel: 0491155900
   Fax: 0491155905
   E-mail: sofitel.marseille@sofitel.com

