Location
     __________________________________________________________________

   Surrounded by the city’s most iconic landmarks, the Sofitel Marseille
   Vieux Port is in an ideal location for both visitors and inhabitants.
   The historic Panier neighbourhood, the Old Port, the city centre and
   the seafront are all within comfortable walking distance…
